---
title: "sciter-create-component — Sciter Adapter Delta"
---
%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant S as Skill
    participant Mem as AgentMemory
    participant FS as FileSystem
    participant Preview as PreviewApp

    note over S,SSIM: Phases 0,1,1.5,4,5 — follow create-component.mmd unchanged
    note over S,SSIM: This diagram shows Sciter-specific overrides only

    note over S: Pre-Phase 2 — load agent memory
    S->>Mem: read .claude/agent-memory/sciter-create-component/feedback_*.md
    Mem-->>S: known fixes (typography, icon centering, layout tips)
    note over S: apply known fixes before generating CSS/JS

    note over S: Phase 2 Stream B — Sciter CSS/JS overrides
    note over S: dip units 1:1 from Figma px (never px)<br/>flow: horizontal | vertical (not display: flex)<br/>width: * (not flex: 1)<br/>overflow: none (not overflow: hidden)<br/>@mixin typography; (no font shorthand with var())<br/>no comma in @mixin values<br/>class Name extends Element (no functional)<br/>class not className<br/>__DIR__ + "img/..." icon paths (not "./img/")<br/>imports require .js extension

    note over S: Phase 3 — adapter.visual_verify() expansion

    S->>FS: tools/fetch-figma-screenshot.sh <fileKey> <nodeId> /tmp/figma-<name>.png
    FS-->>S: PNG at 2x scale, absolute bounds
    S->>FS: copy → tools/ScreenshotHistory/{ts}_figma_{name}.png

    loop max 3 attempts
        S->>Preview: tools/preview-component.sh <preview.js> <Name> <width> /tmp/figma-<name>.png
        note over Preview: internally: captures screenshot + runs find-component.py --direct
        note over Preview: window stays open — Space toggles Figma overlay
        Preview-->>S: SSIM score + /tmp/component-compare.png + /tmp/component-diff.png

        alt SSIM >= 0.95
            note over S: PASS — exit loop
        else SSIM < 0.95
            S-->>U: show diff + score + region description
            U-->>S: explanation of discrepancy
            S->>FS: apply targeted CSS/JS fix
        end
    end

    alt passed (SSIM >= 0.95)
        S->>FS: copy /tmp/preview-screenshot.png → ScreenshotHistory/{ts}_code_{name}.png

        opt fix was applied during retries
            S->>Mem: write .claude/agent-memory/sciter-create-component/feedback_ssim_<topic>.md
        end
    else EC14 — still < 0.95 after 3 attempts
        note over S: Level 1 — user explains root cause
        S-->>U: side-by-side comparison + SSIM progression + region delta
        U-->>S: explanation

        alt fix resolves the issue
            S->>FS: apply fix, re-run SSIM once
            S->>Mem: write feedback_ssim_<topic>.md
        else systematic pattern
            S-->>U: Level 2 — draft rule change proposal<br/>(show proposal only — do not write to file)
        end

        opt tool limitation or script bug
            S-->>U: Level 3 — structured bug report<br/>Component accepted with status: needs-review
        end

        S->>FS: copy /tmp/preview-screenshot.png → ScreenshotHistory/{ts}_code_{name}.png
    end
